org.apache.ambari.server.configuration

Class AmbariServerConfigurationProvider<T extends AmbariServerConfiguration>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.configuration.AmbariServerConfigurationProvider<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.inject.Provider<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AmbariLdapConfigurationProvider, AmbariTProxyConfigurationProvider, JwtAuthenticationPropertiesProvider

    public abstract class AmbariServerConfigurationProvider<T extends AmbariServerConfiguration>
extends Object
implements com.google.inject.Provider<T>
    AmbariServerConfigurationProvider is an abstract class to be extended by Ambari server configuration provider classes.

    This implementation registers for the following Ambari server events to help load the relevant properties when available and/or updated:

    • AmbariConfigurationChangedEvent
    • JpaInitializedEvent
